\begin_inset Formula $\vartheta\colon\mathfrak{m}^{2}\to R$
\end_inset

 defined by
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vartheta(x_{1},x_{2}):=\theta(x_{1}+x_{2})-\theta(x_{1})-\theta(x_{2}),
\]

\end_inset

lands in 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathfrak{m}$
\end_inset

.
 
